message: Update build and core library for purescript 0.7
Update dependencies, fix warnings, better re-exports, clean up some other stuff
Add a no-op to HalogenF; squash HalogenF into a sum type

Switch EventSource to use purescript-stalling-coroutines

This will allow users to filter event sources. This is meant to resolve
 #233
add 'bower install' to scripts, bump purescript dependency to 0.7.6
Fix warnings, make all event handlers use Maybe
Restore ajax example test, update dependencies
Fix build/test scripts for new pulp
Update build scripts & PS version dependencies
Remove last js file in favour of unsafe-refs, drop eslint

Avoid linking examples for much faster CI builds

The examples are still buildable as individual projects, but now when
run from the root of the project we build against the main output dir

Add i18n/reflection example (#427)

* Add i18n/reflection example

* Fix HOC name

* Add i18n to test runner
Update dependencies and syntax for PureScript 0.11
Remove i18n example - without Given it's not useful

Add namespaces for examples

Sometimes weird things can happen when batch-building the examples,
since some module names are reused across examples but have differing
content.

Migrate project to Spago (#653)

Switches the Halogen repository to use Spago as the package manager, including switching all examples to be Spago-based. With this update it also removes all references to Bower.

Uses a new Bower file generated by Spago. This is the same as the old one, as far as Pursuit / publishing is concerned, but with one change: it now includes effect explicitly as a dependency. It was already included transitively via several other dependencies, so including it isn't really a change.

Also deletes the GUIDE.md link, as the /docs folder has been around for years now and there are no links to this file within the repository.
There are no changes to the underlying library or other code outside of simple tweaks needed to make sure everything's up to date.

Halogen 6 (#723)

* Remove `surface` parameter

* `f` -> `q` type variable in examples

* Use event rather than coroutines

* Use `tell` or `request` directly to raise queries

* Simplify handlers by removing `Maybe` return value

* Add a variant of slot to ignore child output

* remove Maybe from onFileUpload (#662)

* Add handler' to exports (#697)

* Replace `id_` with `id`

* Add migration guide for Halogen 5 -> Halogen 6 (#720)

* Support Purescript 0.14 (#721)
